   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VytVrS25.33 (ms. 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>aṣ̌a.ciθra āiiese yešti</em> pas harw xšnūman kē bēd guftan <em>iməm haōməm
               uzdātəm</em> tā gyāg dō bār guftan agar xšnūman ahlawān padiš bēd <em>auuaŋ́hā̊
               frauuaṣ̌aiiō</em>…</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent"> "<em>aṣ̌a.ciθra āiiese yešti</em>. Afterwards, they should recite
            wahtever <em>šnūman</em> it is. They have to recite <em>iməm haōməm uzdātəm</em> until
            this passage two times. If the <em>šnūman</em> contains the <em>ahlawān</em>, (they have
            to recite:) <em>auuaŋ́hā̊ frauuaṣ̌aiiō</em>…"</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
